       0000-MAIN-PROCESS               SECTION.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
           MOVE WHEN-COMPILED          TO WRK-WHEN-COPILED.

           PERFORM 1000-INITIALIZE.

           PERFORM 2000-PROCESS-FILE UNTIL WRK-FILE0001-EOF EQUAL 'END'
                                     AND   WRK-FILE0002-EOF EQUAL 'END'.

           PERFORM 3000-FINALIZE.
